nt|Folkestone]]''', [[Kent]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Boulogne-sur-Mer]]''', [[Pas-de-Calais]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Glasgow]]''' and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Marseille]]''', [[Bouches-du-Rh\u00f4ne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Gloucester]]''', [[Gloucestershire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Metz]]''', [[Moselle (department)|Moselle]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Godalming]]''', [[Surrey]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Joigny]]''', [[Yonne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Hailsham]]''', [[East Sussex]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Gournay-en-Bray]]''', [[Seine-Maritime]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Hammersmith and Fulham]]''', [[London]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Boulogne-Billancourt]]''', [[Hauts-de-Seine]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Harrogate]]''', [[Yorkshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Luchon]]''', [[Haute-Garonne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[London Borough of Harrow|Harrow]]''', [[London]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Douai]]''', [[Nord (French department)|Nord]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Hastings]]''', [[East Sussex]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[B\u00e9thune]]''', [[Pas-de-Calais]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[London Borough of Havering|Havering]]''', [[London]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Hesdin]]''', [[Pas-de-Calais]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Hereford]]''', [[Herefordshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Vierzon]]''', [[Cher (department)|Cher]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Herne Bay, Kent|Herne Bay]]''', [[Kent]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Wimereux]]''', [[Pas-de-Calais]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[London Borough of Hillingdon|Hillingdon]]''', [[London]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Mantes-la-Jolie]]''', [[Yvelines]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Horsham]]''', [[West Sussex]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Saint-Maixent-l'Ecole]]''', [[Deux-S\u00e8vres]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[London Borough of Hounslow|Hounslow]]''', [[London]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Issy-les-Moulineaux]]''', [[Hauts-de-Seine]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Inverness]]''' and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Saint-Valery-en-Caux]]''', [[Seine-Maritime]]\n* {{flag