a Chapelle-Saint-Mesmin]]''', [[Loiret]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Northampton]]''', [[Northamptonshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Poitiers]]''', [[Vienne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Norwich]]''', [[Norfolk]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Rouen]]''', [[Seine-Maritime]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Oxford]]''', [[Oxfordshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Grenoble]]''', [[Is\u00e8re]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Perth, Scotland|Perth]]''' and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Cognac, France|Cognac]]''', [[Charente]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Plymouth]]''', [[Devon]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Brest, France|Brest]]''', [[Finist\u00e8re]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Portsmouth]]''', [[Hampshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Caen]]''', [[Calvados (department)|Calvados]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Preston, Lancashire|Preston]]''', [[Lancashire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[N\u00eemes]]''', [[Gard]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Ramsgate]]''', [[Kent]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Conflans-Sainte-Honorine]]''', [[Yvelines]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Reigate and Banstead|Reigate]]''', [[Surrey]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Brunoy]]''', [[Essonne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[London Borough of Richmond upon Thames|Richmond upon Thames]]''', [[London]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Fontainebleau]]''', [[Seine-et-Marne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Rochdale]]''', [[Greater Manchester]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Tourcoing]]''', [[Nord (French department)|Nord]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Rotherham]]''', [[Yorkshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Saint-Quentin, Aisne|Saint-Quentin]]''', [[Aisne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Royston, Hertfordshire|Royston]]''', [[Hertfordshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[La Loupe]]''', [[Eure-et-Loir]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Borough of Runnymede]]''', [[Surrey]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Joinville-le-Pont]]''', [[Val-de-Marne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[City of Salford|Salford]]''', [[Greater Manchester]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Clermont-Ferrand]]''', [[Puy-de-D\u00f4me]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Salisbury]]