y of Southampton]]''', [[Hampshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Le Havre]]''', [[Seine-Maritime]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Southborough, Kent|Southborough]]''', [[Kent]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Lambersart]]''', [[Nord (French department)|Nord]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Borough of Spelthorne|Spelthorne]]''', [[Surrey]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Melun]]''', [[Seine-et-Marne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[St Albans]]''', [[Hertfordshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Nevers]]''', [[Ni\u00e8vre]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Stalybridge]]''', [[Tameside]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Armenti\u00e8res]]''', [[Nord (French department)|Nord]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Stevenage]]''', [[Hertfordshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Autun]]''', [[Sa\u00f4ne-et-Loire]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Stockport]]''', [[Greater Manchester]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[B\u00e9ziers]]''', [[H\u00e9rault]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[City of Sunderland|Sunderland]]''', [[Tyne & Wear]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Saint-Nazaire]]''', [[Loire-Atlantique]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[London Borough of Sutton|Sutton]]''', [[London]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Gagny]]''', [[Seine-Saint-Denis]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Taunton]]''', [[Somerset]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Lisieux]]''', [[Calvados (department)|Calvados]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Truro]]''', [[Cornwall]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Morlaix]]''', [[Finist\u00e8re]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[London Borough of Waltham Forest|Waltham Forest]]''', [[London]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Saint-Mand\u00e9]]''', [[Val-de-Marne]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Watford]]''', [[Hertfordshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Nanterre]]''', [[Hauts-de-Seine]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Wellington, Shropshire|Wellington]]''', [[Shropshire]] and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Ch\u00e2tenay-Malabry]]''', [[Hauts-de-Seine]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Wembury]]''', [[Devon]]shire and {{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Locmaria-Plouzan\u00e9]]''', [[Finist\u00e8re]]\n* {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Wetherby]]''', [[Yorkshire]] 