dex.php?europe-plus-friendly-disagreement-between-the-french-and-english-the-role-of-culture-in-international-affairs \"French \u2013 English: 100 Years of \u201cFriendly Disagreement?\"], ''Europeplusnet'' (2004)\n* Serodes, Fabrice. \"'Historical use of a caricature. The destiny of the perfidious Albion.\", Brussels, VUB, 2009.\n* Serodes, Fabrice ''Anglophobie et politique de Fachoda \u00e0 Mers el-Kebir'' (L Harmattan, 2010)\n* Serodes, Fabrice \"Brexit: le Royaume-Uni sort, ses id\u00e9es restent\", ''The Conversation'', 17 January 2017\n\n==External links==\n* {{Commonscat-inline|Relations of France and the United Kingdom}}\n* [http://www.francobritishcouncil.org.uk/links.php Franco-British Council Links]\n* [http://www.ulip.lon.ac.uk/ University of London in Paris (ULIP)]\n* [http://www.ambafrance-uk.org/spip.php?page=sommaire&id_rubrique=2 French Embassy in the United Kingdom]\n* [http://ukinfrance.fco.gov.uk/fr/ British Embassy in France]\n\n{{Foreign relations of France}}\n{{UK bilateral relations}}\n{{Portal bar|Politics|France|United Kingdom}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:France - United Kingdom Relations}}\n[[Category:Bilateral relations of the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:Bilateral relations of France|United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:English history-related lists|Wars, France]]\n[[Category:France\u2013United Kingdom relations| ]]\n[[Category:France-related lists|Wars, England]]\n[[Category:French military-related lists|Wars, England]]\n[[Category:United Kingdom military-related lists|Wars, England]]\n[[Category:Military history of Europe]]\n", "name_user": "159753", "label": "safe", "comment": "In French, we use the term vice anglais to refer to homosexuality.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/France%E2%80%93United_Kingdom_relations"}
{"title_page": "ETL Group", "text_new": "{{Infobox company\n| name = ETL Group\n| logo = [[File:ETL Logo.svg|250px|ETL-Gruppe]]\n| type = Group of companies, the most prominent being\n* ETL AG Steuerberatungsgesellschaft\n* ETL AG Wirtschaftspr\u00fcfungsgesellschaft\n* ETL Rechtsanw\u00e4lte GmbH\n| founded = 1971\n| location_city = [[Essen]] / [[Berlin]]\n| location_country = [[Germany]]\n| key_people = Franz-Josef Wernze (CEO)<ref>[https://www.welt.de/regionales/koeln/article108964598/Ein-Rheinlaender-sagt-US-Firmen-den-Kampf-an.html A Rhinelander throws down the gauntlet to US companies], Die Welt, 4 September 2012</ref>\n| num_employees = 7,000 (2015)\n| revenue = over \u20ac650 million (total revenue 2015)\n| industry = [[Tax]] and [[Legal advice]], [[Auditing]], [[management consulting|Management Consultancy]], [[Financial Services]]\n| homepage = {{URL|www.etl.de}}\n}}\n\nThe '''ETL Group''' is a multinational [[corporate group|group of companies]] providing [[tax]], [[legal advice|legal]], [[auditing]] and [[management consulting|management consultancy]] services. It is Germany's largest [[tax advice|tax advisory]] company,<ref>[http://www.focus.de/finanzen/steuern/steuerexperten-im-test-das-dilemma-der-effizienten-kanzleien_id_3770948.html These are Germany's top tax advisors], FOCUS-MONEY, 15 April 2014</ref>  with an annual turnover of over \u20ac730 million (2015), putting it among the top five auditing and tax advisory companies in the Federal Republic.<ref>[http://luenendonk-shop.de/out/pictures/0/lue_pi_wp-liste_f160715%281%29_fl.pdf L\u00fcnendonk list of the \"Leading auditing and tax advisory companies in Germany\"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122232720/http://luenendonk-shop.de/out/pictures/0/lue_pi_wp-liste_f160715%281%29_fl.pdf |date=2017-01-22 }} as of 16 July 2015, consulted on 26 January 2016</ref><ref>[http://www.business-on.de/koeln-bonn/etl-gruppe-interview-mit-franz-josef-wernze-unternehmensgruender-und-vorstandsvorsitzender-der-etl-gruppe-_id38467.html Interview with Franz-Josef Wernze] in Business-On</ref><ref>[http://www.etl.de/zeigepdf/pdf.presse/Karriere-bei-ETL-Interview-mit-Vorstand-Marc-Mueller Interview with Marc M\u00fcller], WISU 10/2013</ref>\n\nThe ETL Group employs 7,000 partners and staff, including more than 1,400 tax advisors, lawyers, auditors and management consultants. Currently, the group has some 158,000 clients in about 790 offices across Germany. Additionally, the ETL Group operates in almost 50 countries throughout the world under the \"ETL Global\" brand.\n\n== History ==\nAt the beginning of the 1970s, Franz-Josef Wernze and Klaus F. K. Schmidt joined forces to open a tax advisory office.<ref>[http://www.wallstreet-online.de/nachricht/7037759-ehrenpreis-etl-gruender-franz-josef-wernze Award for ETL founder Franz-Josef Wernze], Wallstreet Online, 26 September 2014</ref> The services they offered were soon extended beyond mere tax advice. Wernze and Schmidt took a holistic approach that combined tax advice with auditing and legal services in a one-stop consultancy package. Since 1995, the group of companies providing these services has been operating under the \"ETL\" brand.<ref>[https://register.dpma.de/DPMAregister/marke/register/395129249/DE The German Patent and Trade Mark Office Register], consulted on 26 January 2016</ref>\n\n== Services ==\nThe ETL Group offers consultancy services for [[natural person|private individuals]], [[freelancer]]s as well as [[small and medium-sized enterprise]]. These services are available for all questions regarding tax, legal, economic, organizational and financial issues. Customized consultancy and strategy concepts have been developed for [[petrol station]] proprietors, [[health care professionals]], [[hotel]] and [[restaurant]] owners, [[farmers]] and [[foresters]], [[franchising]], [[senior citizen]]s and [[professional athletes]].\n\nThe [http://felix1.de/ felix1.de] AG Steuerberatungsgesellschaft, launched in 2014, focuses on target groups with a higher affinity for the online world and complements classical consultancy services with digital components such as online identification.\n\n== Group Structure ==\nUnder the holding company ETL AG Steuerberatungsgesellschaft, Essen, the ETL Group is the largest tax advisory company in Germany. Within the Group it is the ETL AG Steuerberatungsgesellschaft together with subsidiaries \n* Freund & Partner GmbH Steuerberatungsgesellschaft, [[Berlin]],\n* RCU Verm\u00f6gensverwaltung AG, [[Essen]], and\n* eurodata AG, [[Saarbr\u00fccken]],\n\nthat carry out the central holding functions. These include, for instance, key strategic decisions as well as the financial, investment and risk management for the whole group.\n\nTax advisory services are pooled in the Freund & Partner GmbH Steuerberatungsgesellschaft corporate division, whereas sector-specific software solutions as well as data centre capacities are provided in an independent corporate division under the leadership of eurodata AG. The RCU Verm\u00f6gensverwaltung division also provides complementary consultancy and financial services with a focus on professional tax advisors as its target group.\n\nThe Group's legal advice sector and auditing activities are coordinated by ETL Rechtsanw\u00e4lte GmbH, Essen, together with ETL AG Wirtschaftspr\u00fcfungsgesellschaft, Berlin.\n\nUnder the brand \"ETL Global\" ETL's international partners cooperate in more than 120 offices worldwide whenever their clients need advice on cross-border activities. Apart from this cooperation network, \"ETL Global\" also encompasses the shareholdings of the ETL Group in European markets, such as Austria, the Czech Republic, Spain, Poland, Great Britain and the Netherlands.\n\n== Social Responsibility and Sports Sponsorship ==\nIn 2008 the ETL foundation \"Kindertr\u00e4ume\" was created.<ref>[http://www.etl-kindertraeume.de/ ETL Foundation website]</ref> Since then over 200 projects have been carried out across Germany to support children in need as well as sick children and teenagers.<ref>[http://koeln-nachrichten.de/gesellschaft/spenden/25-000-euro-fuer-ein-komplettes-spielezimmer/ Example: Donation to children's hospital in Cologne] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160211114749/http://koeln-nachrichten.de/gesellschaft/spenden/25-000-euro-fuer-ein-komplettes-spielezimmer/ |date=2016-02-11 }}, K\u00f6ln Nachrichten, 1 September 2015</ref>\nThe ETL Group is also actively involved in the promotion of popular and [[professional sports]] via a division which is a separate entity from the consultancy services within the group.<ref>[http://www.viktoria1904.de/sponsoren/exklusiv-partner Examples:  Viktoria K\u00f6ln 1904 e.V. website] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329145204/http://www.viktoria1904.de/sponsoren/exklusiv-partner |date=2016-03-29 }}, [http://www.lok-leipzig.com/sponsoren/sponsoren-und-partner/ 1. FC Lokomotive Leipzig e.V. website], [http://www.sglida-handball.de/unser-bus.html SG Linden-Dahlhausen Handball e.V. website] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160211114820/http://www.sglida-handball.de/unser-bus.html |date=2016-02-11 }}</ref>\n\n== Literature ==\n* ETL \u2013 European Tax & Law, Essen 2010, {{ISBN|978-3-00-033425-2}}\n* ETL - 25 Jahre Freund und Partner, 2016, {{ISBN|978-3-00-052083-9}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.etl.de ETL Group website]\n* [http://www.etl-global.com/en ETL Global website]\n* [https://www.felix1.de Felix1 website]\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n[[Category:Management consulting firms of Germany]]\n[[Category:Accounting firms of Germany]]\n[[Category:Companies based in North Rhine-Westphalia]]\n[[Category:Financial services companies established in 1971]]\n[[Category:Consulting firms established in 1971]]\n[[Category:1971 establishments in West Germany]]\n[[Category:Lechia Gda\u0144sk sponsors]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox company\n| name = ETL Group\n| logo = [